by having him jump down the stairs.</i>

6
00:00:48,297 --> 00:00:52,426
<i>He put his son on the second stair
and said, "Jump, and I'll catch you. "</i>

7
00:00:52,468 --> 00:00:56,347
<i>Then on the third stair, and said,
"Jump, and I'll catch you. "</i>

8
00:00:56,388 --> 00:00:59,975
